headline: Earnings update: Zoom, Virgin Galactic, Nvidia, Warner Bros Discovery and more
summary: CFOs, including Gunnar Wiedenfels of Warner Bros Discovery and Colette Kress of Nvidia, addressed disciplined spending, sharper personalization and AI strategy on last month's earnings calls.
